name: PS-15. MetaBall-Delaunay
description:
v4W.ENko - "PS-15. MetaBall-Delaunay" continues the basic "Metaball algorithm" generated in connection with "Delaunay Triangulation" for the "Pattern Standardization" series.  The centers of the "MetaBall" structure are generated with the 10 moving vertices. The color is showing the changes in the lenght of the splines. Abstract streams of the live structure.
Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 180 frames.
